00:50:42,920 --> 00:50:43,989
Có,  nhiều lắm.

501
00:50:44,400 --> 00:50:45,469
Tôi là Lucky Luke.

502
00:50:45,720 --> 00:50:47,676
''Lucky Luke và tứ quái Daltons''...

503
00:50:47,920 --> 00:50:49,194
Ý tôi là...

504
00:50:49,920 --> 00:50:51,069
phiêu lưu...

505
00:50:52,000 --> 00:50:53,228
