586
01:00:13,760 --> 01:00:14,988
Anh xin lỗi.

587
01:00:17,120 --> 01:00:18,519
Đừng bao giờ nói xin lỗi.

588
01:00:32,880 --> 01:00:33,869
Cao bồi!

589
01:00:35,000 --> 01:00:36,069
Lucky Luke!

590
01:00:37,640 --> 01:00:39,039
